Generic single-database configuration with PostgreSQL.

Steps to update the db
1. Wipe database (drop and recreate)
cd/backend
psql -U postgres -c "DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS streampage;"
psql -U postgres -c "CREATE DATABASE streampage;"

2. Delete the current initial alembic migration

3. Generate a new migration
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "initial_schema"

4. run the new migration
alembic upgrade head

